lity of a linear matrix inequality,\ncorresponding to the univariate sequence obtained, and finally we solve\nconcretely odd degree cases of the TMP on curves $y=x^\\ell$, $\\ell=2,3$, and\nadd a new solvability condition to the even degree case on the curve $y=x^2$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 Dec 2022 16:26:21 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 26 Apr 2023 23:29:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-28"}
