eam propagation of large eddies from\nthe cavity. It also shows the pairing of coherent structures between the shock\ntrain and the recirculation zone of the cavity.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Dec 2022 01:38:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-29"}
