\\gamma$-rays detected at Src-NE or Src-NW. Furthermore, the\nmultiwavelength observational properties unanimously imply that the SNR--MC\ninteraction occurs mainly in the northeast direction.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 Dec 2022 15:31:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Jan 2023 15:42:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-15"}
